            <div class="requirements-grid">
                <div>
                    <strong>Status</strong>
                    <span>Coming soon</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <strong>Planned methods</strong>
                    <span>Pix, Mercado Pago, PayPal, and manual review options are being evaluated.</span>
